He was  at the Alexandra Palace on the tournament's second night, posing for photographs with the walk on girls as fans in the 2,500-capacity crowd chanted: 'You want some?'

Phil 'The Power' Taylor and Peter 'Snakebite' Wright were among those playing in the first round at the Ally Pally on Friday, and the Wealdstone Raider admitted he's a big fan of the darts.

'I ain't got no fans. I don't believe this. I haven't got no fans. I love darts. This is the first time I've actually been here live,' he said.

